{"tid":1677153,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求介紹日本上網卡","createTime":"2019-10-27T02:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:55.000Z","uid":250903,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"044821e1c4bc964b7e08574392375e2ea9d27748","tid":1677153,"uid":250903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"屋企人黎緊會去4日日本<br />\n想知有無邊隻日本上網卡最好用<br />\n主要係上網 wtsapp打電話用為主<br />\n上網睇話好似3台個張日本7日上網卡性價比係最高<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVqctnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVqctnc.jpg&h=0614051d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他卡都好似好伏 寫話唔限速但去到某個數據用量就限左 好驚會中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望巴絲幫幫手介紹下親身用過而又好用既sim卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ff02d82df0037eccdb65903625df9151a313d","tid":1677153,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"3hk穩陣冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0254504a7f2ed1a11588b01a576ca23c03d5690","tid":1677153,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"用緊 Ultra Sim (Softbank network)，無伏但留意下自己一日用幾多用量先夠。<br />\n佢有 500MB 同 1GB 揀，唔放心就用 1GB 吧，大約 $13/日。"},{"pid":"5763a81d6036f33b12e5957bf204a0eef0bbda38","tid":1677153,"uid":211003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"落ssp叫佢介紹"},{"pid":"f40ec776043b4e91413bbe7a5aa9558fa66b77c7","tid":1677153,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c55ff02d82df0037eccdb65903625df9151a313d","tid":1677153,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"3hk穩陣冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"幾銀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frow